          <div class="ref-label">// Sources &amp; References</div>
          <ul class="ref-list">
            <li>Wikipedia — "Beast of Bray Road": <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beast_of_Bray_Road" target="_blank">en.wikipedia.org</a></li>
